How'd you know I was alone?

01:44.472 --> 01:46.806
Well, he could have
been with me so...

01:49.043 --> 01:50.677
I know, but maybe
try not to completely

01:50.810 --> 01:53.247
destroy my life
the next time you're lonely.

01:54.482 --> 01:56.183
I mean...

01:57.717 --> 02:01.088
Yeah.

02:03.124 --> 02:05.758
Yeah, I set a really
high standard for.

04:30.903 --> 04:32.339
Excuse me.

04:32.473 --> 04:33.540
Ma'am.

04:35.476 --> 04:36.809
Excuse me.

04:38.646 --> 04:40.180
