I was gonna do this.

08:23.303 --> 08:25.806
It would be good to
meet the inspiration

08:25.939 --> 08:27.107
for your next film.

08:27.307 --> 08:29.510
I've already booked
a room for you.

08:29.643 --> 08:32.012
Just wait till you see
the hotel down there.

08:32.145 --> 08:33.614
Oh, I almost forgot.

08:33.747 --> 08:38.151
My sister found this
in my father's safe

08:38.285 --> 08:41.221
when she was going
through his things

08:41.355 --> 08:42.756
and getting them in order.

08:42.890 --> 08:44.491
It's a relic from west baden.

08:44.625 --> 08:46.545
I thought you might find
it useful or interesting

08:46.593 --> 08:48.295
or whatever.

08:48.428 --> 08:51.098
It's the only thing
that survived the crash.

08:59.106 --> 09:00.541
Jesus.

09:37.144 --> 09:38.211
