10:12.145 --> 10:14.314
I like your taste in music.

10:14.448 --> 10:17.684
It's haunting. Nice.

10:17.818 --> 10:22.856
Okay, well, whenever you're
ready, let it all out.

10:22.990 --> 10:24.658
Hopes, dreams, regrets.

10:31.632 --> 10:32.366
Okay.

10:32.499 --> 10:34.134
She can't say I didn't try.

10:40.907 --> 10:42.342
Hello.

10:52.452 --> 10:54.388
You messing with me, Campbell?

11:01.228 --> 11:02.663
Oh, come on.

11:05.832 --> 11:07.000
All right, okay.

11:07.200 --> 11:08.344
That's good. That's a good one.

11:08.368 --> 11:09.870
You got me.

11:12.040 --> 11:13.740
Well, you feel like talking?

11:16.877 --> 11:18.012
Yes.

11:18.146 --> 11:20.247
Holy shit, he speaks.

11:21.149 --> 11:22.416
Pardon my...

11:22.549 --> 11:24.184
It's all right, it's fine.

