the camera, is that right?

11:52.779 --> 11:56.283
Okay, gotta admire your
commitment to the bit.

11:56.416 --> 11:59.286
Tell me about the town.
West baden, is it?

12:00.088 --> 12:03.590
Nice place... to hide.

12:05.992 --> 12:07.360
