21:21.482 --> 21:23.250
Where are you from?

21:24.151 --> 21:25.852
You know, I'm not really in...

21:25.985 --> 21:27.554
Message received.

21:33.594 --> 21:38.265
Sometimes a woman just needs
to drink alone all by herself,

21:38.399 --> 21:40.200
an island.

21:40.334 --> 21:42.436
