21:44.004 --> 21:46.140
and the only real
contact we have anymore

21:46.273 --> 21:48.609
is through
the Internet and email...

21:48.742 --> 21:51.779
- Chicago.
- I love Chicago.

21:51.911 --> 21:55.815
I mean, it's been
years, decades.

21:55.948 --> 21:57.685
Used to take the train
there all the time

21:57.817 --> 22:00.154
with my husband before the kids.

22:01.188 --> 22:03.223
Trains haven't run in years,

22:03.357 --> 22:07.695
but the tracks are still out
back just off the property.

22:07.827 --> 22:09.330
Used to be
the only way in or out

22:09.463 --> 22:12.032
