from out of town.

22:12.166 --> 22:16.570
Now, well, it's almost
too easy to get here, isn't it?

22:20.541 --> 22:21.642
Ann mckinney.

22:21.775 --> 22:24.078
Erica Shaw.

22:24.211 --> 22:26.946
What brings you to
west baden, Ms. Shaw?

22:27.914 --> 22:30.250
- I'm a filmmaker.
- Fancy.

22:30.384 --> 22:33.220
Not really that kind of, um...
It's a documentary...

22:33.354 --> 22:35.855
You're making a documentary
