down for the second time.

22:46.899 --> 22:48.469
Forget about death and taxes.

22:48.602 --> 22:51.705
This hotel is the one true
certainty in west baden.

22:51.839 --> 22:52.939
Yeah?

22:53.140 --> 22:57.578
I mean, look at it. Really look.

22:57.711 --> 23:01.648
Like one of those churches
