33:13.693 --> 33:14.961
obviously.

33:15.162 --> 33:16.472
Now that we're working
together, you know,

33:16.496 --> 33:18.232
this is a really
big deal for me,

33:18.366 --> 33:19.799
collaborating with Erica Shaw.

33:19.933 --> 33:21.610
Are you cool with me calling
this a collaboration?

33:21.634 --> 33:23.246
'Cause this really feels
like a collaboration.

33:23.270 --> 33:26.940
I'm definitely getting, like,
a collaborative vibe happening.

33:27.074 --> 33:28.074
Do you know him?

33:28.242 --> 33:30.011
