33:39.753 --> 33:40.920
I work at the hotel.

33:41.055 --> 33:42.789
I stay at hotel.

33:43.723 --> 33:45.892
- Josiah.
- Erica.

33:47.560 --> 33:48.795
Kellyn.

33:49.763 --> 33:51.098
I'm kellyn, hi.

33:51.232 --> 33:53.300
You play Blackjack?

33:53.434 --> 33:55.702
