34:13.254 --> 34:14.854
Cool, so you actually
own the hotel.

34:14.988 --> 34:18.092
- Oh, wow.
- Yeah.

34:18.225 --> 34:20.894
Yeah, see, you're welcome,
set you up perfectly for that.

34:21.928 --> 34:23.930
Be something though wouldn't it?

34:24.065 --> 34:24.731
What?

34:24.864 --> 34:26.100
Owning that place?

34:27.268 --> 34:29.669
I don't know. It seems
like a lot of work.

34:29.803 --> 34:31.638
Can't even keep
my apartment clean.

34:34.075 --> 34:36.843
- What?
- You don't fool me, Erica from Chicago.

34:36.976 --> 34:39.080
- Oh, no?
- No, you do not.

34:39.213 --> 34:41.881
You can sit there, you know,
act like you're cool,

34:42.016 --> 34:45.152
laid back, but you got it too.

34:45.286 --> 34:49.356
The sickness.
I can see it in your eyes.

34:49.490 --> 34:51.325
What do you mean by that?

34:51.459 --> 34:53.394
You want more than you got.

34:53.527 --> 34:57.031
I know because I have it too.

34:57.164 --> 34:59.233
'Cause this maintenance
thing, I mean,

34:59.366 --> 35:01.135
this is, like,
a temporary kind of...

35:01.268 --> 35:02.979
Look, I've done it all here.
I was a bartender.

35:03.003 --> 35:05.172
I was a mechanic's apprentice.

35:05.306 --> 35:06.866
Blasted limestone
for a couple of years.

35:06.940 --> 35:08.476
- Oh yeah.
- Yeah?

35:08.608 --> 35:10.211
Yep, that is a job. Yes, indeed.

35:10.344 --> 35:12.222
I... actually, I still got
all my gear in the car.

35:12.246 --> 35:13.926
