a wall or something.

35:13.980 --> 35:16.584
Hey, I might take you up
on that one day.

35:16.716 --> 35:19.220
You know, it is what it is.

35:19.353 --> 35:20.963
Be honest with you,
it's the best job I ever had.

35:20.987 --> 35:22.467
The world's designed
to kick your ass,

35:22.590 --> 35:25.226
but you get yourself
a drill, a little dynamite...

35:25.359 --> 35:26.759
You can be your own
force of nature.

35:26.893 --> 35:28.895
Yeah. Why'd you give it up?

35:30.431 --> 35:32.500
