35:32.632 --> 35:35.169
Besides I always knew that
I was meant for bigger shit.

35:36.437 --> 35:37.770
World dominance?

35:39.540 --> 35:42.076
Yeah. Yeah, why not?

35:42.209 --> 35:43.987
I mean, that's right up there
