35:50.584 --> 35:51.985
Bradford?

35:52.119 --> 35:53.563
Well, yeah, I mean, maybe
my name goes on there,

35:53.587 --> 35:56.423
maybe I make some shit up
like Microsoft.

35:56.557 --> 35:58.658
Point is, I got plans, okay?

35:58.791 --> 36:00.027
