36:00.161 --> 36:02.662
sure as hell bigger
than that hotel.

36:03.696 --> 36:05.832
To "Josiah Bradford,
incorporated."

36:19.580 --> 36:21.215
So you grew up in west baden?

36:22.016 --> 36:25.718
- What?
- You... nothing.

36:31.058 --> 36:32.226
What about your family?

36:32.426 --> 36:34.061
You guys been here
the whole time?

36:34.195 --> 36:35.329
My family?

36:35.529 --> 36:37.464
Wait, what are we...
What are we talking about?

36:37.598 --> 36:39.567
Nothing, just...

36:39.699 --> 36:41.901
Look, I didn't mean to...

36:42.036 --> 36:43.736
Some fuckin' room, right?

36:43.870 --> 36:47.675
Yeah. Yeah, everything here's...

36:47.807 --> 36:49.876
You know,
I've lived here forever.

36:50.010 --> 36:51.378
