in one of these rooms.

36:56.450 --> 36:58.085
Must be nice.

36:58.219 --> 36:59.453
Josiah.

36:59.653 --> 37:02.489
I... you know what? I think
I'm gonna go. I'm gonna go.

37:02.623 --> 37:03.623
No, c'mon, stay.

37:03.657 --> 37:05.159
Let's have a drink.

37:05.292 --> 37:06.826
What's that?

37:07.827 --> 37:09.363
Nothing, it's just this thing.

37:09.496 --> 37:11.764
Come on, let's have
a real drink.

37:15.102 --> 37:19.473
Sorry, I didn't mean to pry.

37:19.607 --> 37:23.377
Maybe it's just because you've
lived here your whole life,

37:23.510 --> 37:27.947
but this town...
And maybe it's the hotel...

37:29.816 --> 37:31.218
It really puts you
in a weird place.

37:31.352 --> 37:32.952
And anyway, it's nice
to talk to somebody

37:33.053 --> 37:34.664
who knows what it's like
to grow up in a place...

37:34.688 --> 37:36.257
Ugh, tastes like shit.

37:38.791 --> 37:39.859
Did you just...

37:39.993 --> 37:41.228
Cold as fuck, too.

37:43.863 --> 37:45.999
You know, you really
shouldn't just...

37:51.138 --> 37:53.098
Sorry, I didn't mean...
Sorry, I didn't mean that.

37:53.173 --> 37:55.175
Yeah, maybe you're right.

37:55.309 --> 37:57.278
- What?
- Maybe you should go.

38:06.953 --> 38:09.490
Hey. Hey look, I'm sorry
I didn't mean to do...

38:09.623 --> 38:10.957
- It's fine.
- No, seriously.

38:11.091 --> 38:12.526
I said it's fine.

38:17.964 --> 38:19.433
What? What is it?

38:21.035 --> 38:22.603
Nothing. You should go.

38:22.736 --> 38:24.971
- Erica.
- Go!

38:50.164 --> 38:51.444
Look, Campbell,
you're just gonna

38:51.532 --> 38:53.833
- have to accept the realities.
- Quiet.

39:05.079 --> 39:06.447
Excuse me?

39:06.580 --> 39:08.048
