39:08.182 --> 39:10.417
Wondering if you
could help me out.

39:10.551 --> 39:11.984
Have you seen him?

39:12.119 --> 39:14.188
Wanted for murder,
possible kidnap.

39:14.321 --> 39:15.988
Still might have
that boy with him.

39:16.123 --> 39:18.092
Perhaps a closer look
will help you.

40:16.283 --> 40:17.785
And the thing no one tells you

40:17.917 --> 40:21.088
about being detail orientated
is that you have to see

40:21.221 --> 40:24.158
the big picture first
in order to see anything,

40:24.291 --> 40:25.893
in order to get
anything accomplished.

40:26.026 --> 40:27.327
Oh, look who it is.

40:27.528 --> 40:29.996
Are we a definite yes
on the festival, yet?

40:30.130 --> 40:31.832
Oh, I just have to
check my schedule.

40:31.964 --> 40:33.200
Long night?

40:35.935 --> 40:37.137
Excuse me?

40:37.337 --> 40:40.607
No, it's just
you seem a little...

40:40.741 --> 40:43.043
I guess I better
get back to my work.

40:43.177 --> 40:45.078
It looks like someone
needs the water.

40:49.116 --> 40:50.851
Sorry?

40:51.118 --> 40:54.288
First time guests get a complimentary
session in our mineral baths.

40:54.421 --> 40:57.524
Now they say the water here is
magical for a number of reasons.

40:57.658 --> 41:02.229
But first and foremost,
it's the perfect hangover cure.

41:10.970 --> 41:15.709
Yeah, that sulfur smell lets
you know it's the real deal.

41:15.843 --> 41:17.144
I mean, the pluto water company

41:17.344 --> 41:19.379
started pasteurizing
this stuff in the '30s

41:19.513 --> 41:21.048
to give it more of a shelf life.

41:21.181 --> 41:22.883
Some say that killed
the waters magic,

41:23.016 --> 41:26.553
but not this stuff, it is
straight from the spring.

41:34.695 --> 41:35.963
So what do you say?

41:36.096 --> 41:38.232
Ready for a rebirth of your own?

41:39.833 --> 41:41.368
Maybe some other time.

41:42.035 --> 41:44.505
Sure. Sure.

41:44.638 --> 41:46.773
The water's certainly
not going anywhere.

42:14.301 --> 42:17.437
What the fuck, man?
Still down here!

42:56.910 --> 42:58.245
Something nice about it.

42:58.845 --> 43:01.081
The past.

43:01.214 --> 43:02.983
Stick around long
enough you lose

43:03.116 --> 43:05.152
everything you ever loved...

43:06.820 --> 43:12.392
But the past is always
there fully intact.

43:13.061 --> 43:14.394
Perfect.

43:14.528 --> 43:18.066
Just waiting for
you to come home.

43:18.198 --> 43:20.200
Sorry, okay.

43:23.870 --> 43:25.990
Yeah, don't suppose I could
get you to say that again.

43:26.074 --> 43:28.241
- Could I?
- Why?

43:28.375 --> 43:30.410
I just want to separate
you from the wall.

43:30.544 --> 43:32.646
- Oh, um, I think we can make it work...
- No!

43:32.779 --> 43:34.881
And I wanted to make
sure I'm getting...

43:35.016 --> 43:37.784
I'm old, but I'm not stupid.

43:37.918 --> 43:40.587
You didn't come here
for local color.

43:40.721 --> 43:43.490
You wanna know about
Campbell Bradford.

43:46.526 --> 43:47.828
If you're not comfortable...

43:47.961 --> 43:49.396
That's fine.

43:49.596 --> 43:51.865
But you better get the lighting
exactly how you want it

43:51.999 --> 43:55.302
because I'm sure as hell
not say in any of this again.

43:56.269 --> 43:57.838
Fair enough.

43:58.039 --> 44:03.111
Campbell Bradford, hadn't
heard that name for a while.

44:03.243 --> 44:05.679
Doesn't seem to
fade away though.

44:05.812 --> 44:06.880
You knew him?

44:07.081 --> 44:09.916
Well, not personally.
My daddy did though.

44:10.051 --> 44:15.989
Talked about him like the
boogeyman or something worse.

44:16.124 --> 44:17.557
'Cause he was real.

44:17.691 --> 44:21.161
Why can't I find any info
about him or his family?

44:21.294 --> 44:23.997
The bradfords... the ones
around here anyway...

44:24.132 --> 44:29.137
Never could catch much luck
in the longevity department.

44:29.269 --> 44:33.874
Only one I can even think of
is his great-grandson...

44:34.008 --> 44:35.008
Josiah.

44:35.043 --> 44:36.043
We've met.

44:36.144 --> 44:37.411
Yeah.

44:38.712 --> 44:41.281
Kid's been a mess
his whole life,

44:41.415 --> 44:42.983
can't blame him, I guess.

44:43.117 --> 44:44.117
Considering...

44:44.184 --> 44:45.619
Considering what?

44:45.819 --> 44:48.622
Well, having a man like
Campbell in your line...

44:49.256 --> 44:50.490
Can't imagine.

44:50.624 --> 44:53.493
He made his name in blood.

44:53.627 --> 44:56.064
My daddy wouldn't even
look me in the eye

44:56.196 --> 44:57.397
when he'd talk about him.

44:57.531 --> 44:59.700
But he still talked about him.

45:00.734 --> 45:02.235
Why?

45:03.303 --> 45:08.275
Certain stories,
they just refuse to die.

45:09.342 --> 45:10.811
No one could touch him.

45:11.978 --> 45:14.848
Not the law, not anyone.

45:15.782 --> 45:17.751
He thought the town was his.

45:19.519 --> 45:21.722
Couldn't get the hotel though.

45:22.856 --> 45:25.559
The owner refused
to sell it to him.

45:27.694 --> 45:31.531
Didn't think Campbell was
worthy of a place so perfect.

45:31.665 --> 45:33.167
Special.

45:33.300 --> 45:35.169
So Campbell killed him,

45:35.302 --> 45:37.804
beat the owner to death

45:37.938 --> 45:40.640
right in front of
the man's only child.

45:40.774 --> 45:43.643
Then he just took the boy.

45:43.777 --> 45:46.080
Sheriff went looking
for him after that,

45:46.214 --> 45:48.749
but Campbell killed him too.

45:48.882 --> 45:53.820
Even had someone from the FBI
come down from Chicago.

45:53.954 --> 45:56.823
So Campbell finally
skipped town for good,

45:58.291 --> 46:01.028
right after burning him alive.

46:01.162 --> 46:04.865
Found that fed's body in a pile
of ash along the river bank,

46:04.998 --> 46:07.434
but all they ever
found of that child...

46:08.202 --> 46:09.803
Was his violin.

46:12.106 --> 46:13.774
You okay, dear?

46:14.741 --> 46:15.742
Mm-hmm.

46:17.844 --> 46:22.049
Suppose that's Campbell
Bradford in a nutshell.

46:22.183 --> 46:27.420
Kind of person so evil,
you get them in your head,

46:27.554 --> 46:30.258
you start seeing him everywhere.

46:30.423 --> 46:37.064
It's a miracle this hotel...
This town survived him at all.

46:37.964 --> 46:39.666
Maybe they didn't.

46:41.235 --> 46:42.569
What?

46:44.172 --> 46:48.742
Campbell's alive.
Barely, but I've met him.

46:50.111 --> 46:52.779
But that's not possible.

46:55.448 --> 46:59.953
The years and his age,
and it's not...

47:00.087 --> 47:02.789
- Okay, maybe we should take a little break.
- I've met him, Anne.

47:03.690 --> 47:06.693
He's with us for now.

47:13.967 --> 47:15.468
I really don't
mean to press here.

47:15.602 --> 47:18.272
I'd be careful, I were you.

47:18.405 --> 47:19.806
What do you mean by that?

47:19.940 --> 47:23.044
If you don't know
by now, you will.

47:24.045 --> 47:25.846
Maybe he's changed.

47:25.979 --> 47:30.218
- Changed?
- Maybe he found love for god, or...

47:30.350 --> 47:33.020
At my age, one of the only
things I know for sure

47:33.154 --> 47:37.191
is that people,
they don't change.

47:37.325 --> 47:40.660
Just become more of
what they really are.

47:48.269 --> 47:50.604
I get that, I do.

47:50.737 --> 47:53.406
I'm just asking you
to keep an open mind.

47:53.540 --> 47:55.109
Yeah, and I know that
it's your father,

47:55.309 --> 47:58.045
but you're the one who wanted to
know the truth about the story.

47:58.179 --> 48:00.348
You're the one who
wanted to know...

48:00.480 --> 48:03.284
No I understand, I'm not stupid.

48:03.416 --> 48:05.219
Of course.

48:05.353 --> 48:06.920
It's just... okay, all right.

48:07.054 --> 48:08.555
The people around here,

48:08.755 --> 48:11.858
when you mentioned the name
Campbell Bradford, they...

48:11.992 --> 48:13.872
I'm sure you were hoping
for a different version

48:13.927 --> 48:16.063
of this story, but this is it.
This is the...

48:16.197 --> 48:17.673
I'm telling you,
this is so much bigger

48:17.697 --> 48:19.633
than anything you can imagine.

48:21.302 --> 48:22.769
No, you're not hearing me.

48:22.969 --> 48:25.605
The most important thing is for
everybody to know the truth.

48:25.739 --> 48:27.841
That's the most important thing.

48:27.974 --> 48:29.576
And you could have
hired anybody.

48:29.709 --> 48:31.288
